snippet.title: Devilated Official Trailer
snippet.description:
A game by Trung Cao "Trunka".
Devilated is a timeslowing, monster blasting, boomer shooter with RPG pretensions, buckets of blood and a dose of ultraviolence.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/570950/Devilated/
